118.title: Mr. Natural
notes:
Underground comics feature by R. Crumb, which appears in its own title and in several other titles including
  • Hup
  • Plunge into the Depths of Despair
  • Snatch Comics
  • Uneeda Comix
  • Yellow Dog
  • Your Hytone Comics
  • Zap Comix
A continuing character in the Mr. Natural stories is one Flakey Foont.
